Package: CodeSummary
Title: RMarkdown Template for Doctoral Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stefano Forgione
Maintainer: Stefano Forgione <tu@email.com>
Description: General-purpose RMarkdown template for data analysis. Includes 
    sections for data loading, cleaning, statistics, visualization and export, 
    with collapsible interpretation blocks per chunk and a final summary.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
